name: MySQL5

getPSDEDataQueryCodeConds.customCond: FIND_IN_SET ( t1.ID, (select tt.linkStories from zt_story tt where tt.id = ${srfdatacontext('srfparentkey','{"defname":"ID","dename":"ZT_RELEASE"}')}))
getPSDEDataQueryCodeConds.name: 查询条件

queryCode:
SELECT	
	t1.`ID`,	
	t1.`TITLE`,
	t1.STORYSN 
FROM
	`zt_story` t1
	LEFT JOIN zt_module t11 ON t1.MODULE = t11.ID
	LEFT JOIN zt_story t21 ON t1.PARENT = t21.ID
	LEFT JOIN zt_product t31 ON t1.PRODUCT = t31.ID 
	LEFT JOIN zt_branch t41 ON t1.BRANCH = t41.ID
